==Russian==
===Noun===
'''копейка''' (kopéjka) {{f}}, [[копейки]] (kopéjki) {{p}}

#[[kopeck]] (A monetary unit of Russia, 100 of which make up a [[rouble]]. Also, [[kopek]], [[copeck]]).

